<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.3.3">
<l>paṇṭivaṉ veṇṇeyuṇ ṭāṉeṉ ṟāycciyar kūṭiyi ḻippa</l>
<l>veṇṭicai yōrumva ṇaṅka viṇaimaru tūṭuna ṭantiṭ</l>
<l>ṭaṇṭarum vāṉatta varu māyira nāmaṅka ḷōṭu</l>
<l>tiṇṭiṟal pāṭava ruvāṉ cittira kūṭattuḷ ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who appeared so that the herdesses once altogether complained,</l>
<l rend="indent">“He ate the butter,”</l>
<l>Having walked between twined marutu [trees]</l>
<l rend="indent">as those of [all] eight directions bowed,</l>
<l>So that celestials and those of heaven sang of his firm strength,</l>
<l>Along with his one-thousand names, he is the one present in Citrakūṭam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
